### 重温 JS replace 方法

- 基本用法

  ```js
  let pet = 'my little 🦄';
  console.log(pet.replace('little','gaint'))
  ```

- 链式调用
  ```js
  let pet = 'my little 🦄';

  let anotherPet = pet
    .replace('my','your')
    .replace('litter',giant)
    .replace('🦄','🐧');

  console.log(anotherPet) // your gaint 🐧
  ```
- 使用特殊占位符来替换匹配项
